Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end
if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
muly B/0.05
pen gs_cont_pen
material hemat add -A*.5, -0.025, zzyzx-0.05 brick a,0.05,0.05 del 1
material cumat
if iOpOrientation = ONE_SIDE then addz 0.05 addx -a*.5 x=a*(pc*.01) k=a/(wc-0.005) if fra(k)>0 gosub 10
for l=1 to k-1 addx x/k gosub 20 next l else addz 0.05 addx -a*.5 x=a*(pc*.01) k=a/(wc-0.005) if fra(k)>0 gosub 10
for l=1 to (k*.5) addx x/k gosub 20 next l del top addz 0.05 addx a*.5 for l=1 to (k*.5) addx -x/k gosub 20 next l endif
end
10: k=int(k)+1 return
20: rotz ac addx -wc*.5
brick wc,0,zzyzx-0.125
del 2 return
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen add2 -a/2,0 mul2 1, B/0.05
rect2 0,-0.025,a,0.025
line2 0,0,a,0 hotspot2 a/2,0.025 hotspot2 0,-0.025 hotspot2 a,-0.025 hotspot2 a/2,-0.025 hotspot2 0,0.025 hotspot2 a,0.025
fill gs_fill_type POLY2_B 5, 2+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, 0,0.025,1, a,0.025,1, a,-0.025,1, 0,-0.025,1, 0,0.025,1
if iOpOrientation = ONE_SIDE gosub 5 if iOpOrientation = BOTH_SIDES gosub 6 end
5:
x=a*(pc/100) k=a/(wc-0.005) if fra(k)>0 gosub 10
for l=1 to k-1 add2 x/k,0 gosub 20 next l del top mul2 1, B/0.05 line2 (a/2)-0.15,-0.1,(a/2)-0.05,-0.075 line2 (a/2)-0.15,-0.05,(a/2)-0.05,-0.075 return
6: x=a*(pc/100) k=a/(wc-0.005) if fra(k)>0 gosub 10
for l=1 to (k/2) add2 x/k,0 gosub 20 next l del top mul2 1, B/0.05 add2 a/2,0 for l=1 to (k/2) add2 -x/k,0 gosub 20 next l del top mul2 1, B/0.05 line2 -0.15,-0.1,-0.05,-0.075 line2 -0.15,-0.05,-0.05,-0.075 line2 0.15,-0.1,0.05,-0.075 line2 0.15,-0.05,0.05,-0.075 return
10: k=int(k)+1 : return
20: rot2 ac
add2 -wc/2,0 ! brick wc,0,c-0.125 line2 0,0,wc,0 del 2 return
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
!Hide all parameters from UI hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
values{2} "iOpOrientation" ONE_SIDE, `1 Сторона`, BOTH_SIDES, `Обе Стороны`
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
LOCK "b"
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_shadow"
values "pc" range [0, 100]
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
! const values for parameter: iOpOrientation ONE_SIDE = 1 BOTH_SIDES = 2

! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "StyleAndDimensionsPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ pageStartY = 0 _infHeight = 19 _outfHeight = 15 _yOffset = 4 xPict = 56 yPict = 136 PictWidth = 361 PictHeight = 42 dy = 24 x1 = 0 x2 = 170 x3 = xPict - 28 x4 = xPict + 77
_yCurr = pageStartY ui_infield{3} "iOpOrientation", x2, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight, 8, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `1 Сторона`, ONE_SIDE, "", `Обе Стороны`, BOTH_SIDES ui_tooltip `Направление Открывания`
_yCurr = _yCurr + _yOffset ui_outfield `Направление Открывания`, x1, _yCurr, x2 - 2, _outfHeight
_yCurr = _yCurr + dy - _yOffset ui_infield "pc", x2, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Жалюзи Закрыты (%)`
_yCurr = _yCurr + _yOffset ui_outfield `Поворот Ламелей`, x1, _yCurr, x2 - 2, _outfHeight ui_outfield `%`, x2 + 63, _yCurr, 27, _outfHeight
_yCurr = _yCurr + dy - _yOffset ui_separator x1, _yCurr, 444, _yCurr
if iOpOrientation = ONE_SIDE then ui_pict 1, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_VerticalBlind_Style1.png else ! BOTH_SIDES ui_pict 2, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_VerticalBlind_Style2.png endif
_yCurr = yPict - _infHeight - 2 ui_infield "wc", x3, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Ширина Ламелей` ui_infield "pc", x4, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Жалюзи Закрыты (%)`
return
